## Output Format

Generate tests using pytest style:

```python
import pytest

class Test<Feature>:
    """Tests for <feature>."""

    def test_<scenario>_returns_expected_result(self):
        """Test that <scenario> produces <expected result>."""
        # Arrange
        ...

        # Act
        result = ...

        # Assert
        assert result == expected
```
